## рџ”§ Tech Stack

| Component | Choice | Rationale |
|-----------|--------|-----------|
| **LLM** | Gemini 2.0 Flash (free tier via `google-genai`) | Fast (sub-5s), free 1500 req/day, good at structured JSON output |
| **Embeddings** | `sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2` | Free, local, no API calls вЂ” fast cold start, good quality |
| **Vector Store** | FAISS (in-memory, ~377 vectors) | Zero infra, instant retrieval, fits in memory easily |
| **Framework** | FastAPI + uvicorn | Required by spec |
| **Deployment** | Render free tier (Docker) | Free, auto-sleep, /health wake-up (2 min grace) |

