## рџ›ЎпёЏ Risk Mitigations

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| Gemini rate limits | Gemini 2.0 Flash free tier: 15 RPM, 1500/day вЂ” sufficient for eval |
| Hallucinated URLs | Post-process: validate every URL against catalog lookup dict |
| Slow response (>30s) | Use Flash (fast model), pre-computed embeddings, keep prompt concise |
| Schema non-compliance | Pydantic strict validation + fallback parsing |
| Cold start >2 min | Pre-build FAISS index at Docker build time, lazy-load model |
| Off-topic/injection | System prompt with explicit refusal + input length cap |

